<h1>Send a message</h1><? if ($errors) { ?><ul class="error"><? foreach ($errors as $error) { ?><li><?=$error?></li><? } ?></ul><? } elseif($form_to == "ml_bug_report") { ?><p>You are about to file a bug report or make a suggestion.&nbsp; If you're filing a bug report, please be very specific when describing what went wrong and make sure you include the following:</p><ul>	<li>What browser you are using, and what operating system</li>	<li>A detailed description of the problem</li>	<li>A link to the page where the error occurred</li>	<li>Steps to reproduce the problem</li></ul><p>This information will help the developers track down the source of the problem and get it fixed faster.&nbsp; Thanks!</p><p>If you're making a suggestion, please be very specific in describingwhat should be changed/added to the site to make it better, and why.</p><? } elseif ($form_to == "ml_abuse" ) { ?><p>You are about to file an abuse report.&nbsp; Please note that we take the security of The Campus Bullet <strong>very seriously</strong>, and if we find that the post or account violates the terms of use, the account and/or IP address of the offending account will be banned.&nbsp; Also, please be very specific in identifying the offending account or content.</p><? } else { ?> <p>Welcome to the message center!&nbsp; You can message any of The Campus Bullet moderators using this tool.&nbsp; (Any account that begins with ml_)</p><? } ?><div id="contact"><form method="POST" action=""><input type="hidden" name="action" value="message" /><table><tr>	<th>To:</th>	<td><? if ($fixed_recipient) {		?><input type="hidden" name="to" value="<?=$form_to?>" /><?		if ($form_to == "ml_bug_report") echo "MasterList Code Monkeys";		elseif ($form_to == "ml_abuse") echo "MasterList Abuse Police";		else echo $form_to;	} else { ?>		<input type="textbox" name="to" value="<?= $form_to ?>" />	<? } ?>	</td></tr><tr>	<th>Message:</th>	<td><textarea name="message" style="width: 500px; height: 200px"><?= $form_message ?></textarea></td></tr><tr>	<th></th>	<td><input type="submit" value="Send message" /></tr></table></form></div>